text: Lamin Jawo (born 15 March 1995) is a Gambian footballer who plays for Czech club FC Fastav Zlín. ==Career== ===Club career=== After a trial at FC Vysočina Jihlava in January 2019, the club announced on 29 January, that the player had signed a contract until June 2020.Lamin Jawo podepsal kontrakt v FCV, fcvysocina.cz, 29 January 2019 On 21 January 2020, he was bought free by Czech First League club FC Fastav Zlín, where he signed a three-year deal.DO ZLÍNA PŘICHÁZÍ GAMBIJSKÝ ÚTOČNÍK LAMIN JAWO: „MÉ NEJVĚTŠÍ PŘEDNOSTI?
